trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Contiene un insieme di istanze della classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da aggiungere a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Aggiunge un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The position at which the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> was inserted.
trans-unit.target: Posizione in cui è stato inserito l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da individuare in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> contains a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina se <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> contiene un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> specifico.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se il valore del parametro <paramref name="header" /> si trova in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensionale che rappresenta la destinazione degli elementi copiati dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: La matrice deve avere un'indicizzazione in base zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in the <c>array</c> parameter at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Indice in base zero nel parametro <c>array</c> a partire dal quale viene effettuata la copia.

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> to an <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at a particular index of the <see cref="T:System.Array" />.
trans-unit.target: Copia gli elementi dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> in un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Array" />, cominciando da un particolare indice di <see cref="T:System.Array" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Il valore del parametro <paramref name="array" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: Il parametro <paramref name="index" /> è minore di zero.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is multidimensional.
trans-unit.target: Il parametro <paramref name="array" /> è multidimensionale.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: oppure

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source SoapHeaderCollection is greater than the available space from the <paramref name="index" /> parameter to the end of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: Il numero degli elementi dell'oggetto SoapHeaderCollection di origine è maggiore dello spazio disponibile dal parametro <paramref name="index" /> alla fine della matrice di destinazione.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da individuare in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines the index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina l'indice dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The index of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter, if found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: Indice del parametro <paramref name="header" />, se disponibile nell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; in caso contrario, -1.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Indice in base zero in corrispondenza del quale inserire <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to insert into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da inserire in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Inserisce un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> in corrispondenza dell'indice specificato.

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter equals the number of items in the collection, then the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> is appended to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Se il `index` parametro è uguale al numero di elementi nella raccolta, il <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> viene aggiunto alla fine della raccolta.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elementi dopo il punto di inserimento spostati verso il basso per consentire il nuovo elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameteris not a valid index in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Il parametro <paramref name="index" /> non è un indice valido nell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to get or set.
trans-unit.target: Indice in base zero dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da ottenere o impostare.

trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in corrispondenza dell'indice dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> specificato.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in corrispondenza dell'indice specificato.

trans-unit.source: This property provides the ability to access a specific element in the collection by using the following syntax: `myCollection[index]`.
trans-unit.target: Questa proprietà consente di accedere a un elemento specifico della raccolta utilizzando la sintassi seguente: `myCollection[index]`.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameteris not a valid index in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Il parametro <paramref name="index" /> non è un indice valido nell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> da rimuovere da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Rimuove la prima occorrenza di un elemento <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> specifico dalla classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> gli elementi che seguono l'oggetto rimosso <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> spostare verso l'alto occupare la posizione rimasta vuota.
